originalText.text: Dr. Rossi is the best Mohs surgeon I have ever encountered. His patience, kindness and professional approach is flawless. I cannot recommend Dr. Rossi and his team enough.

originalText.text: Dr. Rossi and his team were amazing.  Very knowledgeable and up to date on the newest procedures  and studies available.   They spent time explaining my procedure and answering any questions I had along the way.   Without hesitation I would recommend Dr. Rossi .

originalText.text: Dr Rossi is an incredibly talented dermatologist. Along with his extensive, in-depth research and work experience, he's also exceptionally warm, personable and an attentive listener. He presents all available options (including cutting edge tech/treatments) and then tailors solutions to your particular needs, and answers all the questions you have at every step of the way. Extra bonus is that he takes time to check in on you after consultations and treatments.
